{"tid":212153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急!認真POST!] 救唔救到隻貓睇你地啦!!!!","createTime":"2017-04-22T08:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T10:13:41.000Z","uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c22652d8c0cf446e54101632bbdb1dcb1bc60b42","tid":212153,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 時事台既連登巴打,我開係寵物台冇乜人睇,唯有借你地個場黎出POST,希望可以比多啲人睇到.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>事源 : </strong></span><br />\n呢條友成日都會責怪領養貓「泰山」,又會厭佢太生猛,會同佢本身隻家貓「多多」隻揪嘈交,之後日日困隻「泰山」係籠入面,基本上「泰山」係籠外面既生活一日據佢主人之前啲POST係得一個鐘既活動時間放出籠,如果你話做完手術,要困幾日唔好比佢整爆個傷口絕對冇問題,但條友係日日都困鳩住隻「泰山」,養殖場時刻都困鳩住啲狗冇分別,你咁撚樣同將佢坐監有乜撚野分別,越困鳩佢,佢只會壞反感.不如放返佢出去流浪佢仲開心自在,又會開叫春POST係度話想要既係一隻乖乖聽話既貓,而唔撚係搞事....大概既內容就係下圖,佢之前既FACEBOOK POST已經del左,我搵唔返啲圖,<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我有半句吹水屈鳩佢,我絕子絕孫,冚家鏟  </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/m50tDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fm50tDz.png&h=98f9c91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/5uHrom.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F5uHrom.png&h=c4367d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/W2dyQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FW2dyQJ.jpg&h=f2d9d2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/2ym6Va.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F2ym6Va.png&h=09e8d11b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/eQw1gn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FeQw1gn.png&h=2dc30c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/BGWxpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FBGWxpw.jpg&h=3210a795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/lAoszj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FlAoszj.jpg&h=8c6cbafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/4dpoXC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F4dpoXC.png&h=68487823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/A3eF2B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FA3eF2B.jpg&h=93e3471e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/90MHr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F90MHr8.jpg&h=c51eea79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事主已經將昨日嘴炮既Facebook Post delete,希望有好心人接走隻流浪貓「泰山」,唔好再比佢過坐監既生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5139d90fa7c189ada13ca26f8db79369e4b6705","tid":212153,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"8f0747389bcef458e15205807a5b5bbd0710f4e3","tid":212153,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"f32629f15e3df0a52e74fbc547c2ba3ce2ee0fac","tid":212153,"uid":3645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"7876368671282893db25436f0f60e536b57b53fd","tid":212153,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T08:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edca73bf6ce12d418d9d5b384216